In South Pembrokeshire, south of the Ritec Fault, the Lower ORS is represented by, in ascending order, the Freshwater East, Moors Cliff, and Freshwater West formations. These are [unconformably](/Unconformity) overlain by the Ridgeway Conglomerate Formation. The Middle ORS is absent, while the Upper ORS is represented by the Gupton and West Angle formations.

